name: Yoshgramm-wen Light Hull Kit
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct Yoshgramm-wen designed hulls of destroyer-class and below.

name: Yoshgramm-wen Heavy Hull Kit
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct Yoshgramm-wen designed hulls of cruiser-class and above.

name: Yoshgramm-wen Strikecraft Kit
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct Yoshgramm-wen designed strikecraft.

name: Yoshgramm-wen Light Arsenal Kit
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct small-size and some medium-size weapons from Yoshgramm-wen Yards's arsenal catalogue.

name: Yoshgramm-wen Heavy Arsenal Kit
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct medium-size and large-size weapons from Yoshgramm-wen Yards's arsenal catalogue.

name: Yoshgramm-wen Dronecraft Kit
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct restricted unmanned and automated equipment designed by Yoshgramm-wen Yards.
